      • simulateOurWorkLoad

        public void simulateOurWorkLoad()
        This simulates the work our so called "Loader" would be doing, this increments the splash screen. This would technically be replaced by our loading tasks which would incremented the splash loader appropriately. This may be replaced all together by a new class which has a sole purpose of initializing our program.
